Description:
  Generates a new SubmissionRunner template. Pass the language name to the generator, along with a file extension

Example:
  `rails generate submission_runner ruby --ext rb`

  creates a SubmissionRunner template for Ruby:
    create  lib/submission_runners/ruby.rb
      gsub  lib/submission_runners/ruby.rb
      gsub  lib/submission_runners/ruby.rb
    create  spec/lib/submission_runners/ruby_spec.rb
      gsub  spec/lib/submission_runners/ruby_spec.rb
      gsub  spec/lib/submission_runners/ruby_spec.rb
      gsub  spec/lib/submission_runners/ruby_spec.rb
